      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/vr-rh-index-5pt",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Relative Hemolysis Index — 5-point flow-speed validation",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) compared against in-vitro measurements at five operating points (2 L/min–4000 rpm through 6 L/min–2000 rpm). Mean absolute error 0.043 RH units; all predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Mesh independence confirmed at 12.4 M cells (GCI < 1.2 %).",
      "passFailStatus": "Pass",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/vr-rh-index-5pt-uq",
        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
        "method": "GCI Richardson extrapolation plus Monte Carlo propagation of inlet boundary condition uncertainty (±5 % flow rate, ±50 rpm speed). 95th-percentile prediction interval: RH ± 0.11.",
        "coverageProbability": 0.95
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/vr-shear-stress-distribution",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution — PIV comparison",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements obtained on a scaled acrylic replica of the FDA generic pump at 3500 rpm, 4 L/min. CFD wall shear stress distributions compared against PIV-derived estimates at 48 measurement planes. Normalised RMS deviation 6.8 %; peak shear stress predicted within 9 % of PIV reference. Turbulence model sensitivity study (k-ω SST vs. realizable k-ε) showed < 3 % difference in hemolysis index.",
      "passFailStatus": "Pass"
    },
    {
