      "rationale": "Validation experiments used a Newtonian blood analogue (glycerol-water mixture) rather than human blood, consistent with FDA guidance for hemolysis bench testing. Sample-to-sample variability in analogue preparation assessed at ±1.5 % viscosity. Formal test sample statistical analysis not required at MRL 2 for non-biological fluid."
    },
