      "rationale": "COU simulations use identical geometry and fluid properties to validation experiments. Operating point envelope fully overlaps validation matrix. Dimensionless parameters (Reynolds number range 1800–9500, flow coefficient 0.08–0.22) are matched between validation and COU conditions. Formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2 given direct geometric and parametric correspondence."
    }
